2 Section 3. Section 77-2-105, MCA, is amended to read:
3 "77-2-105. Termination of easements. Whenever lands granted for any of the purposes mentioned
4 in 77-2-101(2) 77-2-101(8) through (11) cease to be used for those purposes, the easement terminates upon
5 notice to that effect to the person to whom the grant was made, served at the person's last-known post-office
6 address."
